      "role": "user",
      "content": "the way you say \"let it catch up with you\" ... it's like you're saying it's actually okay to just give up. but if i stop, my whole life is just gone. the career, the identity, everything i've built. it feels like there's no version of the future where this doesn't just end in total failure or misery. it's like i'm trapped in this loop of failing and trying to fix it, and i just want the loop to stop.",
